<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    </header>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
            <p class="mini-title">Meet the Team</p>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Learn more about our team, our project, and why we created HelpHub.
            </p>

            <div class="nav-row">
                <a href="/" class="nav-btn">Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="section-card">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div>
                    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>
                        We are a hackathon team focused on building a simple and useful tool
                        that helps people find community resources more easily. Our goal was
                        to create a website that feels welcoming, easy to use, and helpful
                        for people looking for Food support, Shelter help, campus resources,
                        and Donation centers.
                    </p>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        Our mission is to make support easier to find by organizing local
                        resources in one simple place.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-box">
                    <div>
                        <img src="/images/image.png" alt="Team Photo">
                    </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-card">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Paul Conner</h3>
                    <p>Project Lead: Assisted in all parts. <br> Back End Developer: Programmed Dynamic Functions</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Jennifer Mejia</h3>
                    <p>Data Abstractor: Gathered all information as needed.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Benjamin Loeffler</h3>
                    <p>UI Designer: Designed the layout, colors, buttons, etc.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Joseph Lustre</h3>
                    <p>UI Designer: Designed the layout, colors, buttons, etc.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-card">
            <h2>Why We Created HelpHub</h2>
            <p>
                We created HelpHub because finding help should not feel confusing
                or overwhelming. We wanted to make a website that is simple, clear, and practical
                so users can quickly find resources without wasting time.
            </p>
            <p>
                This project represents our effort to support the community through technology
                by making important information easier to access.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>